title: Sins of the Father
description: An old friend of Derek's is brought up on child abuse charges after he is found with his son covered in bruises. Nick also reveals a darkly kept family secret of his own.

title: Town Without Pity
description: Nick discovers an anomaly having to do with a colony that disappears and re-appears seemingly every 50 years and asks to investigate further.

roles.char: Nakties Davisia, Mistress of Endless Night

title: The Twelfth Cave
description: Randolph Hitchcock, a friend of Derek's, donates an ancient manuscript from the 12th cave of the Dead Sea scrolls. Nick & Phillip discover the scroll is not what it seems. Also, Alex investigates a haunting at a Victorian B&B.

title: She's Got the Devil in Her Heart
